0in%201979%2C%20the%20Education%20Department%20has%20played%20a%20critical%20role%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20individual%20students.%20Trump%20has%20suggested%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-student-loans-moving-to-sba-away-from-education-department-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoutsourcing%20the%20department's%20responsibilities%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20other%20federal%20agencies%2C%20but%20some%20experts%20say%20that%20other%20agencies%20%E2%80%94%20already%20tasked%20with%20many%20of%20their%20own%20responsibilities%20%E2%80%94%20are%20not%20equipped%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-reshaping-americas-schools-investigations-funding-cuts-department-of-education-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emanage%20the%20Education%20Department's%3C%2Fa%3E%20vast%20funding%20and%20student%20aid%20network.%20Splitting%20up%20the%20functions%20could%20put%20the%20programs%20that%20millions%20of%20students%20rely%20on%20at%20risk%2C%20they%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20them%2C%20Title%20I%2C%20has%20provided%20grants%20for%20low-income%20school%20districts%20since%201965.%20Title%20I%20funds%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffelt-guilty-not-signing-kids-up-after-school-activities-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eafter-school%20and%20summer%20programs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20teacher%20professional%20development%2C%20academic%20intervention%20for%20struggling%20students%2C%20tutoring%2C%20and%20more.%20The%20Education%20Department%20allocated%20more%20than%20%2418%20billion%20in%20Title%20I%20funds%20in%20fiscal%20year%202024.%20Trump%20wants%20to%20maintain%20that%20budget%20for%20fiscal%20years%202025%20and%202026%2C%20which%20falls%20below%20the%20funding%20amounts%20Democrats%20have%20pushed%20for%20and%20Biden's%202025%20budget%20request%2C%20which%20called%20for%20%2418.6%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELinda%20McMahon%2C%20Trump's%20education%20secretary%2C%20said%20that%2