s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20places%20are%20going%20to%20be%20as%20nimble%20as%20they%20can%20be%2C%20but%20you%20can't%20open%20an%20after-school%20program%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20August%20with%20a%20week's%20notice%20necessarily%2C%26quot%3B%20Potter%20says.%20Sosa%20said%20that%20in%20July%2C%20his%20district%20already%20saw%20%26quot%3Ba%20small%20reduction%20in%20staffing%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20teachers%20who%20helped%20kids%20catch%20up%20on%20math%20and%20reading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20also%20said%20it%20would%20place%20guardrails%20to%20ensure%20public%20schools%20are%20using%20the%20funds%20in%20ways%20that%20don't%20violate%20executive%20orders%2C%20including%20orders%20designed%20to%20discourage%20%26quot%3Bwoke%26quot%3B%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-wrongly-flagged-jobs-programs-dei-equity-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ediversity%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20inclusion%3C%2Fa%3E%20initiatives.%20This%20means%20that%20although%20the%20funding%20has%20been%20released%2C%20it%20could%20be%20withdrawn.%20Potter%20says%20this%20uncertainty%20could%20cause%20schools%20to%20make%20some%20tough%20decisions%20about%20their%20budget.%20For%20instance%2C%20a%20district%20could%20cover%20the%20pay%20for%20a%20teacher%20who%20focuses%20on%20teaching%20English%20as%20a%20second%20language%20%26quot%3Bby%20shifting%20things%20around%20in%20the%20budget%20and%20stealing%20from%20some%20of%20the%20funding%20that's%20supposed%20to%20cover%20next%20year's%20summer%20programs%2C%26quot%3B%20Potter%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BSo%20maybe%20they're%20able%20to%20keep%20going%20for%20now%2C%20but%20they're%20borrowing%20against%20the%20future%20and%20against%20the%20other%20programs%20that%20they%20need.%26quot%3B%20The%20department%20announced%20on%20September%2015%20that%20it%20was%20repurposing%20funding%20from%20programs%20that%20it%20determined%20%26quot%3Bare%20not%20in