.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fchat-gpt%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChatGPT%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20her%20to%20use.%20Others%20are%20so%20paranoid%20that%20someone%20might%20think%20they've%20used%20AI%20that%20they%20make%20her%20edit%20her%20work%20so%20that%20it's%20%3Cem%3Eextra%20%3C%2Fem%3Eclear%20that%20it's%20human.%20Nassar%20is%20a%20fan%20of%20the%20em%20dash%20%E2%80%94%20unfortunately%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-linkedin-imbotster-syndrome-corporate-writing-work-jobs-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eso%20is%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20clients%20haggle%20with%20her%20over%20it.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20like%2C%20'Can%20you%20get%20rid%20of%20that%3F%20Can%20you%20just%20not%20use%20it%3F'%20I'm%20like%2C%20'Mate%2C%20I've%20always%20used%20this%2C'%26quot%3B%20Nassar%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20London%2C%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENassar%20is%20a%20journalist%20by%20trade%2C%20but%20turned%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdecluttering-side-hustle-makes-money-preferred-over-corporate-job-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoccasional%20freelance%20gigs%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20her%20main%20gig%20after%20being%20laid%20off%20last%20year.%20She's%20ambivalent%20about%20AI.%20She's%20hopeful%20a%20human%20touch%20will%20always%20be%20needed%20for%20the%20type%20of%20work%20she%20does%3B%20she's%20gotten%20good%20at%20writing%20prompts%3B%20and%20regardless%2C%20she%20doesn't%20feel%20like%20she%20has%20a%20choice.%20%26quot%3BMy%20biggest%20fear%20is%20not%20adapting%20and%20then%20being%20left%20behind%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20not%20alone.%20Unlike%20bigger%20companies%2C%20freelancers%20and%20small%20businesses%20can't%20really%20afford%20to%20make%20big%2C%20potentially%20money-losing%20bets%20on%20AI%2C%20but%20they%20can't%20bury%20their%20heads%20in%20the%20sand%2C%20either.%20They%20have%20to%20go%20where%20the%20wind%20blows%2C%20which%20these%20days%20means%20moving%20into%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworkslop-oozing-americas-white-collar-offices-generative-ai-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etech-forward%2C%20decidedly%20messy%20direction%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20freelancers%2C%20entrepreneurs%2C%20and%20academics%20for%20this%20story%2C%20the%20general%20feeling%20I%20got%20was%20they%20think%20that%20while%20AI%20lowers%20the%20barrier%20to%20entry%20for%20small%20operators%20and%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-tools-doubled-income-save-me-fifteen-hours-each-week-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelp%20them%20move%20faster%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20boost%20productivity%2C%20AI%20also%20drives%20down%20wages%20and%20stifles%20creativity%20and%20originality.%20Boasting%20about%20AI%20capabilities%20can%20be%20a%20powerful%20marketing%20tool%2C%20but%20contractors%20also%20feel%20pressured%20to%20do%20more%20for%20clients%20while%20getting%20the%20same%20pay.%20The%20end%20result%3A%20It's%20easier%20to%20get%20a%20foot%20in%20the%20door%20and%20harder%20to%20stand%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20freelance%20economy%20is%20big.%20Bankrate%20estimates%20that%20one%20in%20four%20Americans%20has%20a%20side%20hustle.%20A%20report%20from%20Upwork%2C%20a%20freelance%20marketplace%2C%20found%20that%20skilled%20knowledge%20freelance%20workers%20made%20%241.5%20trillion%20in%202024.%20Cody%20Luongo%2C%20a%20media%20consultant%20based%20in%20Charleston%2C%20South%20Carolina%2C%20recently%20joined%20the%20ranks%20of%20those%20freelance%20professionals%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-market-layoffs-firing-hiring-slowdown-recession-job-listings-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elosing%20his%20job%3C%2Fa%3E.%20AI%20is%20his%20%26quot%3Bconstant%20companion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says%2C%20whether%20drafting%20a%20press%20release%20or%20refining%20a%20pitch.%20He%20thinks%20it%20helps%20him%20close%20the%20experience%20gap%20with%20more%20established%20professionals%20and%20navigate%20scenarios%20he's%20never%20encountered.%20%26quot%3BAI%20accelerates%20my%20work%20enough%20that%20I%20can%20do%20exponentially%20more%20for%20my%20clients%20with%20their%20allotted%20budgets%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20great%20for%20budget-conscious%20clients%20and%2C%20to%20some%20extent%2C%20for%20his%20own%20bottom%20line.%20What%20it%20means%20for%20his%20peers%20overall%20is%20a%20different%20story.%20While%20AI%20allows%20more%20side%20hustlers%20to%20enter%20the%20market%2C%20it%20can%20also%20make%20the%20endeavor%20less%20lucrative%2C%20thanks%20to%20competition%20from%20other%20freelancers%20and%20from%20AI%20itself%2C%20as%20clients%20consider%20a%20project%20and%20think%2C%20%26quot%3BEh%2C%20I%20bet%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-index-indeed-skills-jobs-change-roles-immune-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20robots%20can%20do%20it%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20reduces%20hiring%20and%20pay%20for%20freelancers%20whose%20skills%20overlap%20with%20its%20capabilities%2C%20according%20to%20research%20by%20a%20group%20of%20professors%20out%20of%20Washington%20University.%20After%20ChatGPT's%202022%20release%2C%20the%20number%20of%20jobs%20for%20writing-related%20freelancers%20on%20Upwork%20fell%20by%202%25%20and%20monthly%20earnings%20fell%20by%205.2%25.%20Freelancers%20who%20work%20in%20images%20%E2%80%94%20designers%2C%20editors%2C%20artists%20%E2%80%94%20saw%20their%20opportunities%20fall%20even%20more%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-image-generators-artists-copying-style-thousands-images-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDALL-E%20and%20Midjourney%20came%20out%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Jobs%20fell%20by%203.7%25%20and%20income%20by%209.4%25.%20The%20fall-off%20was%20steeper%20for%20freelancers%20who%20produce%20higher-priced%2C%20better-executed%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20drop%20in%20earnings%2C%20if%20anything%2C%20is%20actually%20larger%20for%20high-quality%20freelancers%20in%20comparison%20with%20low-quality%20freelancers%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Xiang%20Hui%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20of%20marketing%20at%20Washington%20University%20and%20one%20of%20the%20academics%20behind%20the%20research.%20%26quot%3BHigh%20quality%20doesn't%20really%20protect%20freelancers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELess-experienced%20freelancers%20are%20able%20to%20punch%20up%20their%20work%20with%20AI%2C%20flooding%20the%20marketplace%20with%20cheaper%20stuff%20that%20clients%20may%20find%20%26quot%3Bgood%20enough.%26quot%3B%20There's%20still%20an%20obvious%20difference%20between%20%26quot%3Bgood%20enough%26quot%3B%20and%20truly%20great%20work%2C%20but%20the%20shrinking%20of%20the%20gap%20while%20the%20price%20difference%20remains%20the%20same%20means%20more%20experienced%20people%20lose%20part%20of%20their%20competitive%20edge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20definitely%20lowers%20the%20barrier%20to%20entry%2C%20so%20it%20makes%20many%20activities%20accessible%20for%20more%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Hui%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENick%20Loper%2C%20who%20runs%20the%20website%20Side%20Hustle%20Nation%20%E2%80%94a%20community%20for%20part-time%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fben-hawes-side-hustle-coach-teaches-entrepreneurs-find-niche-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eentrepreneurs%20and%20side%20hustlers%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20tells%20me%20he%20noticed%20someone%20on%20his%20site%20who%20has%20an%20AI%20headshot%20company.%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20shoot%2C%20that's%20my%20wife's%20side%20hustle%2C%20taking%20pictures%20of%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says%2C%20but%20instead%20of%20charging%20%24300-%24400%20for%20a%20half-hour%20session%20for%20human-taken%20headshots%2C%20the%20new%20entrant%20charges%20%2429%20and%20asks%20the%20client%20to%20%26quot%3Bupload%20a%20bunch%20of%20selfies%20that%20it%20spits%20back%20out%26quot%3B%20as%20headshots.%20It%20may%20look%20a%20little%20weird%20%E2%80%94%20or%20unrealistically%20better%2C%20if%20the%20AI%20photo%20editor%20is%20extra%20kind%20%E2%80%94%20but%20people%20seeking%20out%20a%20deal%20might%20decide%20the%20price%20is%20worth%20the%20fake-ish%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20experience%20and%20expertise%2C%20AI%20is%20a%20two-sided%20coin.%20For%20this%20story%2C%20I%20spoke%20with%20one%20PR%20professional%20who%20says%20the%20technology%20has%20allowed%20her%20to%20expand%20into%20hosting%20events.%20She's%20able%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20draft%20invite%20copy%2C%20reminders%2C%20and%20panel%20questions%20and%20to%20create%20recaps%2C%20produce%20videos%2C%20and%20compile%20attendee%20lists%20after%20the%20fact.%20She%20charges%20more%2C%20too%20%E2%80%94%20instead%20of%20invoicing%20%24200%20an%20hour%20for%20three%20hours%20of%20work%2C%20%24600%20total%2C%20she%20charges%20%241%2C200%20for%20the%20whole%20AI-enhanced%20shebang.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20flipside%2C%20I%20heard%20from%20a%20marketer%20who%20complained%20that%20freelance%20platforms%20are%20now%20flooded%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworkslop-oozing-americas-white-collar-offices-generative-ai-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI-generated%20job%20postings%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20applications.%20There's%20%26quot%3Bno%20sense%20in%20crafting%20a%20perfect%20pitch%20to%20a%20client%26quot%3B%20these%20days%20because%20it%20will%20compete%20with%20AI%20pitches.%20I%20also%20heard%20from%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fetsy-witch-spell-ai-slop-economy-consumer-spending-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEtsy%20witch%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20said%20she's%20%26quot%3Bdrowning%26quot%3B%20in%20an%20ocean%20of%20what's%20obviously%20AI%20competition%20%E2%80%94%20everything%20looks%20the%20same%2C%20with%20stereotypical%20images%20and%20suspiciously%20similar%20names.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20so%20frustrating%20knowing%20that%20these%20bots%20are%20preying%20on%20people%20who%20seek%20genuine%20spiritual%20guidance%20and%20receive%20something%20far%20from%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20Whatever%20your%20beliefs%2C%20I%20imagine%20that%20if%20you're%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpsychic-price-cost-spending-habits-economy-psychology-tarot-astrology-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epaying%20for%20a%20psychic%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you'd%20rather%20it%20be%20the%20%26quot%3Breal%26quot%3B%20thing%20than%20whatever%20ChatGPT%20is%20coming%20up%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20workers%2C%20whether%20freelance%20or%20full-time%2C%20AI%20has%20become%20an%20important%20tool%20in%20their%20work.%20Designers%20and%20coders%20can%20use%20it%20for%20organization%2C%20ideation%2C%20and%20client%20quotes.%20Canva%2C%20a%20graphic%20design%20platform%2C%20says%20its%20younger%20users%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20are%20reliant%20on%20AI%20for%20tasks%20such%20as%20brand%20design%20and%20data%20analysis.%20But%20someone%20letting%20on%20that%20they're%20leaning%20on%20AI%20may%20undercut%20how%20the%20work%20is%20perceived%2C%20fairly%20or%20not.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EUsing%20AI%20is%20still%20considered%20taboo%20in%20many%20professional%20fields%2C%20particularly%20in%20creative%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20people%20believe%20work%20is%20produced%20with%20AI%2C%20they%20tend%20to%20reduce%20compensation%20for%20it%2C%20explains%20Shane%20Schweitzer%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20of%20management%20and%20organizational%20development%20at%20Northwestern%20University's%20D'Amore%20McKim%20School%20of%20Business.%20The%20quality%20of%20the%20work%20doesn't%20matter%3A%20People%20hold%20the%20same%20exact%20thing%20in%20less%20esteem%20when%20they%20think%20AI%20was%20involved%20in%20its%20creation.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20just%20think%20they%20deserve%20less%20credit%2C%26quot%3B%20Schweitzer%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20somewhat%20unfair%20%E2%80%94%20a%20product%20is%20a%20product%2C%20however%20it's%20made.%20But%20it's%20also%20understandable.%20While%20many%20workers%20and%20leaders%20position%20AI%20use%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsc%2Fai-desktops-make-workers-productive%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20productivity%20boost%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20others%20see%20it%20as%20a%20cheat%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fphys.org%2Fnews%2F2025-05-people-ai-colleagues-lazier.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20sign%20of%20laziness%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20much%20as%20the%20quality%20may%20sometimes%20be%20comparable%2C%20anyone%20who's%20used%20ChatGPT%20or%20other%20AI%20tools%20knows%20it%20can%20fall%20short.%20AI%20also%20relies%20on%20previously%20created%20material%2C%20which%20can%20homogenize%20output.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20can%20raise%20the%20baseline%20of%20creativity%2C%20but%20fewer%20people%20are%20having%20breakthroughs.%20You%20need%20breakthroughs%20for%20innovation%2C%26quot%3B%20Schweitzer%20says.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20leveling%20the%20playing%20field%20necessarily%2C%20it's%20just%20creating%20slightly%20more%20competence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20main%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-transforming-technical-work-vercel-julius-developers-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Earguments%20in%20favor%20of%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20that%20it%20handles%20mundane%20tasks%20and%20frees%20people%20up%20to%20do%20the%20more%20creative%2C%20interesting%20work.%20That's%20true%20of%20many%20side%20hustlers%20I%20spoke%20to%2C%20who%20used%20it%20for%20the%20boring%20tasks%20most%20everyone%20dreads.%20Lisa%20Driskil%2C%20who%20jokes%20the%20%26quot%3Bonly%20thing%20that's%20not%20for%20sale%20is%20my%20husband%26quot%3B%20in%20her%20eBay%20store%2C%20says%20AI%20saves%20her%20mounds%20of%20time%20in%20writing%20product%20descriptions%20and%20editing%20photos%2C%20especially%20given%20she%20has%20a%20full-time%20job.%20Ross%20Buhrdorf%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20ZenBusiness%2C%20a%20business-in-a-box%20platform%2C%20recently%20launched%20an%20AI%20assistant%2C%20Velo%2C%20that%20supplements%20his%20services%20by%20helping%20people%20navigate%20issues%20such%20as%20taxes%2C%20regulations%2C%20and%20banking.%20For%20small%20business%20owners%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20biggest%20demand%20is%20their%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20His%20company%20%E2%80%94%20now%20accompanied%20by%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20helps%20them%20figure%20out%20the%20logistics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20may%20work%20for%2C%20say%2C%20a%20plumber%20or%20designer%20who%20is%20sick%20of%20invoicing.%20But%20if%20they're%20using%20AI%20to%20learn%20and%20hone%20their%20craft%2C%20that's%20an%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20being%20adopted%20so%20broadly%20that%20it's%2C%20at%20least%20eventually%2C%20going%20to%20prevent%20people%20from%20getting%20and%20using%20key%20skills%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Erin%20Hatton%2C%20a%20sociology%20professor%20at%20the%20State%20University%20of%20New%20York%20at%20Buffalo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreative%20work%20often%20emerges%20from%20iteration%3A%20The%20way%20you%20get%20better%20at%20the%20thing%20is%20by%20doing%20the%20hard%20work%20repeatedly%20%E2%80%94%20generating%20ideas%2C%20working%20through%20tweaks%2C%20taking%20feedback%20into%20consideration%20%E2%80%94%20not%20by%20slightly%20adjusting%20a%20robot's%20version%20of%20the%20thing.%20Moreover%2C%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20the%20side%20hustle%20work%20AI%20is%20creating%20does%20not%20sound%20particularly%20enjoyable%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-content-editing-new-freelance-side-hustle-emerges-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echecking%20the%20AI's%20homework%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20tedious%20endeavor%2C%20and%20the%20technology%20makes%20errors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJinjin%20Qian%2C%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20Strategic%20Finance%20at%20Fiverr%2C%20a%20freelance%20marketplace%2C%20says%20the%20demand%20side%20of%20their%20platform%20has%20changed%20significantly%20due%20to%20AI.%20Instead%20of%20hiring%20someone%20to%20build%20something%20from%20the%20ground%20up%2C%20clients%20use%20ChatGPT%20or%20other%20AI%20tools%20to%20write%20a%20blog%20post%20(or%2C%20in%20one%20case%2C%20a%20novel)%2C%20make%20a%20video%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-limits-learn-to-code-engineers-openai-microsoft-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evibe%20code%20an%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%20themselves%2C%20and%20then%20take%20it%20to%20a%20professional%20to%20get%20it%20across%20the%20finish%20line.%20She%20says%20the%20demand%20for%20simple%2C%20low-end%20jobs%20on%20the%20platform%20has%20plummeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20client%20side%2C%20the%20equation%20is%20pretty%20straightforward%3A%20Getting%20an%20AI%20to%20do%20more%20of%20the%20work%20or%20shifting%20expectations%20in%20the%20name%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvestors-pressuring-companies-to-get-serious-about-ai-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20saves%20money%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGuillermo%20Fernandes%2C%20a%20blockchain%20entrepreneur%20and%20consultant%20based%20in%20New%20York%2C%20tells%20me%20his%20since-sold%20compliance%20startup%20hired%20four%20coding%20interns%20in%202023.%20The%20next%20year%2C%20they%20hired%20only%20one%3B%20the%20rest%20they%20replaced%20with%20AI%20coding%20tools.%20It's%20not%20that%20they%20never%20hired%20freelancers%20again%2C%20but%20when%20they%20did%2C%20they%20were%20true%20%26quot%3Bexperts%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20Carey%20Bentley%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Lifehack%20Method%2C%20a%20productivity%20coaching%20company%2C%20is%20similarly%20eager%20to%20explain%20how%20she's%20been%20able%20to%20cut%20people%20thanks%20to%20AI.%20She%20recently%20got%20rid%20of%20the%20woman%20handling%20their%20email%20newsletters%20after%20determining%20her%20output%20wasn't%20up%20to%20par%2C%20especially%20once%20they%20added%20social%20media%20to%20her%20plate.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20contractor%20I'm%20hiring%2C%20I'm%20looking%20at%20what%20I'm%20paying%20them%2C%20and%20I'm%20thinking%20about%20how%20I'm%20going%20to%20get%20at%20least%20a%203X%20ROI%20on%20this%20person's%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20Anyone%20whose%20fields%20are%20going%20to%20be%20taken%20over%20by%20AI%20needs%20to%20hop%20to%20it%20on%20reskilling%20and%20%26quot%3Bget%20on%20the%20offense%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Fernandes%20and%20Bentley%20are%20service%20providers%20themselves%20%E2%80%94%20the%20plot%20thickens%20when%20the%20shoe%20is%20on%20the%20other%20foot.%20Fernandes%20is%20now%20consulting%20for%20crypto%20and%20blockchain%20companies%20looking%20to%20lobby%20on%20Capitol%20Hill%2C%20and%20he%20works%20faster%20by%20using%20AI%20to%20analyze%20the%20difference%20between%20iterations%20of%20legislation.%20Bentley%20has%20her%20coaches%20record%20conversations%20with%20clients%20and%20then%20put%20them%20into%20AI%20to%20create%20personalized%20summary%20emails%20about%20what%20was%20discussed.%20They%20seem%20OK%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-work-chatgpt-workers-automation-wharton-professor-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproductivity%20hacks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20they%20may%20diminish%20the%20perceived%20value%20of%20their%20services.%20Fernandes%20tells%20clients%20that%20AI%20tools%20are%20why%20he%20charges%20them%20less%20than%20what%20a%20regular%20consultant%20would.%20Bentley's%20clients%20are%20unaware%20that%20their%20personalized%20emails%20are%20generated%20by%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20freelancers%20and%20side%20hustlers%20recognize%20that%20they%20and%20others%20are%20riding%20the%20tiger.%20They%20know%20it's%20dangerous%20%E2%80%94%20they%20just%20think%20it%20won't%20eat%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20people%20in%20creative%20fields%20that%20I%20spoke%20to%2C%20I%20sometimes%20use%20AI%20for%20my%20job%20%E2%80%94%20for%20this%20story%2C%20I%20asked%20it%20if%20my%20opening%20made%20sense%20%E2%80%94%20and%20for%20personal%20questions%2C%20such%20as%20whether%20my%20outfit%20is%20weather-appropriate.%20I%20can%20see%20the%20value%20in%20it%20in%20terms%20of%20productivity%2C%20but%20I%20also%20worry%20about%20what%20it%20means%20for%20the%20ability%20to%20generate%20quality%2C%20original%20work.%20AI%20certainly%20allows%20for%20%3Cem%3Emore%3C%2Fem%3E%20content%20and%20more%20output.%20But%20is%20it%20better%3F%20One%20person%20I%20spoke%20to%20for%20this%20story%20excitedly%20told%20me%20about%20how%20she's%20used%20ChatGPT%20to%20create%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-slop-cultural-renaissance-substack-ceo-chris-best-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrite%20a%20Substack%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Based%20on%20our%20conversation%20it%20seemed%20less%20like%20she%20wanted%20someone%20to%20%3Cem%3Econsume%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethe%20content%2C%20and%20more%20for%20the%20content%20to%20exist%20as%20a%20calling%20card%20or%20line%20on%20her%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%20Perhaps%20the%20best%20case%20I%20hear%20for%20AI%20used%20in%20a%20side%20hustle%20comes%20from%20Kimberly%20Storin%2C%20the%20chief%20marketing%20officer%20at%20Zoom%2C%20who%20also%20happens%20to%20own%20a%20family%20business%20making%20customer%20furniture%20in%20Austin.%20They%20use%20it%20to%20put%20together%20quotes%2C%20find%20materials%2C%20and%20create%20rough%20designs%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20submit%20proposals%20to%20clients%20faster%20than%20the%20competition.%20She's%20lost%20a%20couple%20of%20projects%20where%20the%20AI-generated%20estimate%20was%20probably%20higher%20than%20it%20should%20have%20been%2C%20but%20even%20that's%20valuable%20information%20for%20training%20the%20AI%20to%20get%20better.%20Plus%2C%20she%20can%20use%20Zoom's%20summaries%20of%20internal%20meetings%20at%20the%20shop%20when%20she%20has%20to%20focus%20on%20her%20day%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20opens%20doors%20for%20many%20side%20hustlers.%20It%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20get%20moving%20and%20tackle%20the%20basics%2C%20clearing%20some%20of%20the%20more%20mundane%20administrative%20tasks%20out%20of%20the%20way.%20But%20it's%20not%20the%20fix%20that%20its%20proponents%20often%20cast%20it%20to%20be.%20Researchers%20looking%20at%20the%20broad%20swath%20of%20the%20tech's%20capabilities%20and%20creative%20freelancers%20who%20are%20in%20the%20trenches%20seeing%20AI%20outputs%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%20told%20me%20that%20while%20lifts%20everything%20to%20a%206%2F10%2C%20it%20greatly%20reduces%20the%20chance%20of%20a%209%2F10%20or%2010%2F10%2C%20raising%20the%20floor%20but%20lowering%20the%20ceiling.%20It%20turns%20the%20goal%20in%20many%20projects%20from%20%26quot%3Bgreat%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3BI%20guess%20that'll%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Femily-stewart%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEmily%20Stewart%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%2C%20writing%20about%20business%20and%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fside-hustles-freelance-economy-ai-technology-cheap-income-pay-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1760601781000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68eff824cc993f9955d04483%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fside-hustles-freelance-economy-ai-technology-cheap-income-pay-2025-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AI%20is%20making%20it%20easier%20than%20ever%20for%20Americans%20to%2