and%20partisan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPartially%20as%20a%20result%2C%20the%20market%20for%20alternative%20meat%20has%20fallen.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPlant-based%20food%20is%20struggling%20to%20meet%20this%20political%20moment%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fimpossible-foods-is-at-a-crossroads-with-ceo-peter-mcguinness-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EImpossible%20Foods%20CEO%20Peter%20McGuinness%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20became%20woke%20and%20partisan%20and%20political%20and%20divisive%2C%26quot%3B%20McGuinness%20said%20during%20an%20appearance%20at%20Semafor's%20World%20Economy%20Summit%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcGuinness%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fplant-based-meat%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eplant-based%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20in%20vogue%20right%20now%26quot%3B%20and%20it's%20%26quot%3Bnot%20our%20cultural%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20companies%20like%20his%20can't%20afford%20to%20give%20up%20on%20the%20US%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can't%20give%20up%20on%20the%20US%2C%20because%20it's%20a%20massive%2C%20massive%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20The%20Good%20Food%20Institute%2C%20plant-based%20meat%20and%20seafood%20dollar%20sales%20decreased%207%25%20in%202024.%20The%20decreasing%20consumption%20of%20meat%20alternatives%20is%20partially%20based%20on%20a%20correction%20from%20the%20initial%20hype%2C%20McGuinness%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImpossible%20Foods'%20CEO%20also%20said%20the%20current%20trend%20is%20partially%20a%20result%20of%20how%20the%20original%20marketing%20alienated%20a%20whole%20class%20of%20potential%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20to%20use%20less%20water%2C%20and%20have%20less%20GHG%20emissions%2C%20and%20use%20less%20land%2C%20you%20don't%20target%20vegans%2C%20obviously%2C%26quot%3B%20McGuinness%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20target%20meat%20eaters%20and%20get%20them%20to%20try%20your%20product%2C%20but%20you%20don't%20get%20them%20to%20try%20your%20product%20by%20insulting%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcGuinness%20said%20that%20the%20original%20leaders%20were%20%26quot%3Bzealots.%26quot%3B%20At%20the%20time%2C%20he%20was%20working%20at%20Chobani.%20He%20left%20the%20yogurt%20producer%20for%20Impossible%20Foods%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20beginning%2C%20it%20was%20like%20you%20were%20a%20Neanderthal%20if%20you%20ate%20animal%20meat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20McGuinness%20said%20his%20company%20has%20reoriented%20its%20marketing%20to%20be%20more%20inclusive%20by%20focusing%20on%20the%20quality%20of%20what%20people%20are%20eating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMarketing%20101%2C%20you%20want%20to%20be%20for%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20be%20for%20better%20food%2C%20we%20want%20to%20be%20good%20options.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcGuinness%20is%20also%20trying%20to%20help%20Impossible%20Foods'%20bottom%20line%20by%20pursuing%20international%20expansion%20in%20places%20like%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20where%20he'll%20be%20next%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20whatever%20reason%2C%20consumers%20there%20are%20much%20more%20open%20to%20eating%20plant-based%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20you%20can%20look%20at%20it%20in%20fast%20food%2C%20you%20can%20look%20at%20it%20in%20universities%2C%20high%20schools.%20You%20can%20look%20at%20it%20in%20just%20general%20grocery%20stores%20like%20a%20Tesco%20versus%20a%20Walmart%20or%20a%20Tesco%20versus%20a%20Kroger.%20So%20those%20markets%20are%20pretty%20ripe%20and%20we're%20just%20now%20entering%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fimpossible-foods-sales-consumption-decline-woke-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2