re%20on%20edge%20over%20a%20possible%20AI-fueled%20bubble%20as%20billions%20pour%20into%20the%20technology.%3Cp%3EJOHANNES%20EISELE%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20AI%20gold%20rush%20has%20barely%20begun%2C%20and%20there%20are%20trillions%20on%20the%20line%2C%20Goldman%20Sachs%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EToday's%20AI%20outlays%20are%20small%20compared%20with%20past%20revolutions%20like%20railroads%20and%20the%20internet%2C%20wrote%20analysts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20history%20shows%20first%20movers%20might%20not%20be%20the%20biggest%20winners.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20markets%20may%20be%20fretting%20about%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-ai-bubble-meta-sam-altman-mit-report-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20bubble%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20Goldman%20Sachs%20says%20the%20boom%20is%20still%20in%20its%20opening%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20the%20scale%20of%20current%20investment%20remains%20small%20compared%20with%20the%20potential%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feconomy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eeconomic%20payoff%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20analysts%20at%20the%20Wall%20Street%20giant%20argue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20enormous%20economic%20value%20promised%20by%20generative%20AI%20justifies%20the%20current%20investment%20in%20AI%20infrastructure%20and%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eoverall%20levels%20of%20AI%20investment%20appear%20sustainable%20as%20long%20as%20companies%20expect%20that%20investment%20today%20will%20generate%20outsized%20returns%20over%20the%20long%20run%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20analysts%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs%20in%20a%20Wednesday%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bank's%20analysts%20pointed%20to%20two%20main%20reasons%20for%20their%20call%3A%20AI%20applications%20are%20already%20delivering%20productivity%20gains%20where%20they're%20deployed%2C%20and%20unlocking%20those%20gains%20requires%20massive%20computing%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20estimates%20that%20the%20long-term%20value%20created%20by%20AI%20productivity%20far%20exceeds%20its%20upfront%20costs.%20The%20firm%20projects%20that%20widespread%20AI%20adoption%20could%20add%20%2420%20trillion%20to%20the%20US%20economy%2C%20with%20about%20%248%20trillion%20of%20that%20flowing%20to%20companies%20as%20capital%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGenerative%20AI%20still%20appears%20set%20to%20deliver%20a%20rapid%20acceleration%20in%20task%20automation%20that%20will%20drive%20labor%20cost%20savings%20and%20boost%20productivity%2C%20with%20our%20baseline%20estimates%20suggesting%20a%2015%25%20gross%20uplift%20to%20economy-wide%20US%20labor%20productivity%20following%20full%20adoption%2C%20which%20we%20expect%20will%20realize%20over%20a%2010-year%20period%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analysts%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225dd273e9-f566-466c-939a-5fae6c805b9f%5C%22%3EAI%20investment%20is%20modest%20by%20historical%20standards%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20record-breaking%20spending%20on%20chips%2C%20servers%2C%20and%20data%20centers%2C%20Goldman%20says%20AI%20investment%20is%20modest%20by%20the%20standards%20of%20past%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Ftech%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etechnology%20revolutions.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20estimates%20that%20AI-related%20investment%20in%20the%20US%20is%20under%201%25%20of%20GDP%2C%20compared%20with%20the%202%25%20to%205%25%20of%20GDP%20reached%20during%20earlier%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-bubble-culture-dotcom-housing-crypto-different-vibes-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etechnology%20booms%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20the%20railroad%20expansion%2C%20the%20electrification%20wave%20of%20the%201920s%2C%20and%20the%20dot-com%20era%20of%20the%20late%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman's%20analysts%20said%20they%20still%20see%20the%20macroeconomic%20justification%20for%20AI%20investment%20as%20compelling%20and%20are%20%26quot%3Bless%20concerned%20about%20the%20dollar%20amount%20of%20AI%20capex.%26quot%3B%20They%20noted%20that%20roughly%20%24300%20billion%20is%20being%20spent%20annually%20in%202025%20%E2%80%94%20a%20scale%20they%20view%20as%20appropriate%20given%20the%20technology's%20long-term%20potential%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c7467722-3e6e-4320-aee2-550f5eab5370%5C%22%3EThe%20winners%20may%20not%20be%20today's%20biggest%20spenders%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Goldman%20acknowledges%20%26quot%3Bvalid%20concerns%26quot%3B%20about%20whether%20the%20companies%20pouring%20the%20most%20money%20into%20AI%20will%20ultimately%20reap%20the%20rewards%2C%20especially%20given%20hardware's%20rapid%20depreciation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20analysts%20argue%20that%20timing%20matters%20less%20if%20investors%20can%20capture%20an%20outsize%20share%20of%20AI's%20long-term%20economic%20value.%20But%20history%20suggests%20that%20being%20first%20doesn't%20always%20mean%20finishing%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%20movers%26quot%3B%20could%20fare%20poorly%20in%20infrastructure%20buildouts%2C%20they%20wrote%2C%20citing%20railroads%20and%20telecommunications%20as%20examples.%20In%20many%20cases%2C%20later%20entrants%20captured%20better%20returns%20by%20acquiring%20assets%20cheaply%20after%20an%20early%20overbuild.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20dynamic%20could%20repeat%20in%20the%20AI%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20current%20AI%20market%20structure%20provides%20little%20clarity%20into%20whether%20today's%20AI%20leaders%20will%20be%20long-run%20AI%20winners%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst-mover%20advantages%20are%20stronger%20when%20complementary%20assets%20(e.g.%2C%20semiconductors)%20are%20scarce%20and%20production%20is%20vertically%20integrated%E2%80%94suggesting%20that%20today's%20leaders%20may%20outperform%E2%80%94but%20weaker%20in%20periods%20of%20rapid%20technological%20change%20like%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarly%20adopters%20are%20also%20hedging%20their%20bets%20by%20using%20multiple%20AI%20models%20instead%20of%20sticking%20to%20one%20ecosystem%2C%20which%20could%20weaken%20incumbents'%20advantages%2C%20the%20analysts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20added%20that%20it's%20difficult%20to%20pinpoint%20when%20the%20motivation%20to%20keep%20pouring%20money%20into%20AI%20will%20fade%2C%20since%20early%20productivity%20gains%20and%20steady%20improvements%20in%20model%20performance%20are%20still%20encouraging%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20while%20investment%20should%20eventually%20moderate%20as%20the%20AI%20investment%20cycle%20moves%20beyond%20the%20build%20phase%20and%20declining%20hardware%20costs%20dominate%2C%20the%20technological%20backdrop%20still%20looks%20supportive%20for%20continued%20AI%20investment%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analysts%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman's%20assessment%20lands%20amid%20an%20intense%20debate%20about%20whether%20AI%20has%20inflated%20another%20tech%20bubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20strategists%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-bubble-crash-fears-overblown-valuation-metrics-1999-comparison-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMorgan%20Stanley%20and%20Goldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fa%3E%20argued%20that%20AI%20stock%20valuations%20aren't%20as%20stretched%20as%20critics%20claim%20when%20factoring%20earnings%20growth%2C%20cash%20flow%2C%20and%20profit%20margins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-bubble-boom-goldman-sachs-crash-risk-forecast-outlook-valuation-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1760599618000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f05e761c1f80efbec5aece%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-bubble-boom-goldman-sachs-crash-risk-forecast-outlook-valuation-202