c-openai-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20agents%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20autonomously%20match%20job%20seekers%20with%20hiring%20companies%20has%20raised%20%2420%20million%20in%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELondon-based%20Jack%20%26amp%3B%20Jill%20has%20developed%20two%20conversational%20AI%20agents%20for%20each%20side%20of%20the%20recruitment%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20agent%2C%20called%20Jack%2C%20works%20with%20job%20seekers.%20It%20gathers%20information%20from%20a%20candidate's%20LinkedIn%20profile%2C%20CV%2C%20and%20a%2020-minute%20introductory%20conversation.%20Jack%20then%20searches%20for%20suitable%20jobs%20across%20the%20internet%2C%20provides%20coaching%2C%20and%20conducts%20mock%20interviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJill%2C%20the%20other%20agent%2C%20works%20with%20companies.%20It%20scans%20job%20descriptions%20and%20has%20a%20briefing%20conversation%20with%20the%20in-house%20talent%20team%20to%20understand%20what%20the%20company%20is%20looking%20for%20in%20a%20candidate.%20Jill%20can%20then%20review%20applicants%2C%20source%20candidates%20from%20public%20platforms%20like%20LinkedIn%2C%20and%20conduct%20initial%20interviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20AI%20agents%20can%20also%20interact%20with%20each%20other%20and%20make%20introductions%20over%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20key%20insight%20that%20we%20had%20with%20Jack%20%26amp%3B%20Jill%20is%20that%20AI%20enables%20us%20to%20combine%20the%20nuanced%20understanding%20that%20a%20human%20can%20have%2C%20with%20the%20scale%20that%20you%20can%20get%20from%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20Matthew%20Wilson%2C%20the%20startup's%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilson%20cofounded%20Jack%20%26amp%3B%20Jill%20six%20months%20ago%20with%20Saaras%20Mehan%20after%20they%20became%20frustrated%20with%20what%20they%20saw%20as%20inefficiency%20in%20the%20recruitment%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20says%20it%20has%20more%20than%2049%2C000%20job%20seekers%20using%20its%20