r%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJack%20%26amp%3B%20Jill's%20seed%20round%20was%20led%20by%20Creandum.%20It%20was%20also%20backed%20by%20Dig%20Ventures%2C%20Entrepreneur%20First%2C%20Ada%20Ventures%2C%20Firedrop%2C%20Repeat.vc%2C%20Episode1%2C%20and%20Playfair%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20more%20than%2050%20angel%20investors%20from%20companies%20including%20Lovable%2C%20Anthropic%2C%20and%20ElevenLabs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20plans%20to%20use%20the%20fresh%20funding%20to%20expand%20in%20Europe%20and%20the%20San%20Francisco%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EHere's%20an%20exclusive%20look%20at%20the%20pitch%20deck%20that%20Jack%20%26amp%3B%20Jill%20used%20to%20raise%20its%20%2420%20million%20seed%20round.%20Some%20commercially%20sensitive%20content%20has%20been%20redacted.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jack%20%26amp%3B%20Jill%20pitch%20deck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68efafedcc993f9955d03b63%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJack%20%26amp%3B%20Jill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jack%20%26amp%3B%20Jill%20pitch%20deck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68efafed1c1f80efbec59f20%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJack%20%26amp%3B%20Jill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jack%20%26amp%3B%20Jill%20pitch%20deck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68efafec1c1f80efbec59f1f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJack%20%26amp%3B%20Jill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jack%20%26