feel%20very%20sci-fi.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20that's%20very%20far%20away%20from%20like%20a%20visceral%2C%20like%2C%20'Oh%20man%2C%20this%20is%20gonna%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20that%20people%20used%20to%20do%2C'%26quot%3B%20Altman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFigure%20AI%20is%20facing%20some%20stiff%20competition%20in%20robotics%2C%20mainly%20from%20Tesla%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20who%20has%20a%20rivalry%20with%20Altman.%20Musk%20sued%20OpenAI%20in%202024%20for%20having%20%26quot%3Bdeceived%26quot%3B%20him%20into%20cofounding%20the%20lab%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-elon-musk-ai-lawsuit-sam-altman-harassing-legal-battle-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20countersued%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20harassment%20in%20the%20same%20year.%20In%20September%2C%20Musk%2C%20who%20owns%20xAI%2C%20sued%20Altman's%20company%20again%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-accuses-openai-of-stealing-trade-secrets-in-new-lawsuit-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estealing%20proprietary%20information%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20poaching%20employees%20%E2%80%94%20a%20charge%20the%20company%20has%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20is%20also%20developing%20a%20humanoid%20robot%2C%20Optimus.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20first%20prototype%20was%20showcased%20at%20Tesla's%20AI%20Day%20in%202022%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20Musk%20previously%20said%20the%20robot%20would%20be%20ready%20to%20launch%20%3Cmark%20data-color%3D%5C%22unset%5C%22%3Eas%20a%20customer%20product%3C%2Fmark%3E%20in%20late%202025%20or%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20Figure%20AI%20introduced%20its%20third-generation%20humanoid%20robot%2C%20Figure%2003%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20handle%20household%20chores%2C%20but%20the%20robot%20is%20not%20yet%20available%20to%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20interview%2C%20Benioff%20mused%20about%20whether%20robots%20would%20all%20take%20human%20form%2C%20or%20if%20they%20could%20resemble%20cars%2C%20as%20conceptualized%20in%20the%20%26quot%3BTransformers%26quot%3B%20film%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20robots%20really%20need%20to%20resemble%20humans%20is%20still%20largely%20up%20for%20debate.%20Diligent%20Robotics%2C%20an%20Austin-based%20startup%2C%20builds%20a%20wheeled%20robot%20called%20Moxi%20for%20the%20healthcare%20space.%20It%20doesn't%20have%20legs%20but%20can%20complete%20essential%20chores%20for%20hospital%20staff%2C%20such%20as%20delivering%20lab%20samples%20or%20medical%20supplies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiligent-robotics-vivian-chu-moxi-humanoid-robots-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EVivian%20Chu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20cofounder%20of%20Diligent%20Robotics%2C%20said%20that%20one%20could%20think%20of%20Moxi%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bminimum%20viable%20humanoid%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20less%20complex%20in%20structure%20but%20no%20less%20useful%20in%20comparison%20to%20a%20humanoid%20robot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20think%20that%20over%20time%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20very%20quickly%20see%20that%20the%20wheel%20form%20factor%20%E2%80%94%20like%20two%20arms%2C%20a%20head%2C%20and%20a%20wheel%20%E2%80%94%20is%20probably%20going%20to%20be%20a%20form%20factor%20that%20ends%20up%20covering%20the%20majority%20of%20what%20you%20need%2C%26quot%3B%20Chu%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider's%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELloyd%20Lee%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrett-adcock-figureai-humanoid-robot-new-species-dreamforce-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1760587321000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f031e6cc993f9955d049e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrett-adcock-fig